top_quest_ans_1_expl:
1) The first step is to recognize that there is a lot of unnecessary words in this sentence. You can definitely consider cutting out extra words while maintaining the same context. 
2) You want to avoid using passive voice, and change it to active voice that consists of action verbs instead of verbs like is and was. 
3) You want to avoid using unnessessary verbs like "to go" or "to do" when paired with other verbs like "to camp" and simply use the more specific verb like "to camp".
